---
title: Teriyaki-Glazed Salmon with Jasmine Rice & Sesame-Ginger Veggies
description: Just 30 minutes is all that's standing between you and this delectable dish. There are three simple components: garlic rice, ginger veggies and salmon with an irresistible glaze, and they come together in perfection. You've got this.
